inclusion.criterion: breast cancer confined to breast and lymph nodes under arm
inclusion.label: not_met

inclusion.criterion: surgical removal of tumor with radiation therapy completed or planned
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: tumor expresses estrogen and/or progesterone receptors
inclusion.label: not_met

inclusion.criterion: menstrual period within 6 months before starting chemotherapy for breast cancer
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: menstrual periods stopped for at least 8 weeks starting during or after chemotherapy
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: ovaries surgically removed, treated with radiation therapy, or taking medications (Zoladex™ or Lupron™) to block function of ovaries
exclusion.label: triggers

notes: Patient has MDD and is on anti-depressants for the past 6 months. Her symptoms are still present.
